
This project simply provides singleton-mixin class by using meta-propagation (https://github.com/hipeta/meta-propagate)

Environment:
  sbcl 1.2.1 or higher

Usage:
 1. download meta-propagation (https://github.com/hipeta/meta-propagate) and move it to quicklisp local-project.
 2. download this project from git.
 3. move the directory to quicklisp local-projecct directory.
 4. (ql:quickload :cl-singleton-mixin)
 5. make your-class inherit singleton-mixin and your-class (and subclasses of your-class) become singleton classes.

